  "title": "Environment Agency Chief Regulator’s report 2024-25",
  "body": "\"This Chief Regulator’s report and supporting evidence summarises the performance of the businesses and activities regulated by the Environment Agency in England in 2024 to 2025. It outlines key outcomes of our regulation, providing assurance and transparency across our wide regulatory remit, and it sets out the aims and ambitions of our Chief Regulator.  See the datasets that support this report. \"",
